(55, 31, 'user', 'How many calories should I eat per day?', '2026-03-31 16:18:15'),
(56, 31, 'assistant', 'Your daily calorie target is 1579 kcal, Bianca.\n\nYour calories are set for weight maintenance.\n\nBreakdown:\n- Breakfast: 395 kcal\n- Lunch: 553 kcal\n- Dinner: 474 kcal\n- Snacks: 158 kcal\n\nStick to this target daily for best results!', '2026-03-31 16:18:15'),
(75, 47, 'user', 'What is my workout plan for today?', '2026-04-20 16:39:21'),
(76, 47, 'assistant', 'Your workout plan, john:\n\n- Plan: Male Plan (Full Body Strength)\n- Level: Normal\n- Days per week: 3 days\n- Days completed: 1 / 30\n\nTips for Normal level:\n- Gradually increase reps each week\n- Add resistance or difficulty when exercises feel easy\n- Keep rest periods to 45-60 seconds\n- Track your progress\n\nGo to your Workout page to start today\'s session!', '2026-04-20 16:39:21'),
(89, 37, 'user', 'How many calories should I eat per day?', '2026-04-25 15:00:31'),
(90, 37, 'assistant', 'Your daily calorie target is 1341 kcal, Silagan.\n\nYou are on a calorie deficit to help you lose weight.\n\nBreakdown:\n- Breakfast: 335 kcal\n- Lunch: 469 kcal\n- Dinner: 402 kcal\n- Snacks: 134 kcal\n\nStick to this target daily for best results!', '2026-04-25 15:00:31'),
(91, 37, 'user', 'What should I eat for my Weight Loss goal?', '2026-04-25 15:11:05'),
(92, 37, 'assistant', 'For your Weight Loss goal, Silagan, here\'s what to focus on:\n\nBreakfast: Eggs + oatmeal or whole grain toast\nLunch: Grilled chicken + brown rice + vegetables\nDinner: Fish or lean meat + steamed veggies\nSnack: Fruit, Greek yogurt, or nuts\n\nAvoid: Sugary drinks, fried food, white bread, processed snacks\n\nRemember your daily target is 1341 kcal. Check your Meals page for your personalized plan!', '2026-04-25 15:11:05');

